** '''Player:''' I didn't know rabbits could use magic!
** '''Gregg:''' Of course we can! How else do you think we make Easter happen each year?
** '''Player:''' You make a good point...
** {{tact|previous}}
* {{topt|What am I meant to be doing again?}}
** '''Player:''' So, uh... what am I meant to be doing again?
** '''Gregg:''' You've forgotten already? Silly human!
** '''Gregg:''' We were about to go to Lumbridge to speak to a Cook there who has a lot of eggs!
** '''Gregg:''' We were going to use them to decorate some doors in the spirit of Easter so people associate it less with rabbits!
** '''Player:''' This seems... awfully convoluted.
** '''Gregg:''' Yep!
** {{tact|previous}}
* {{topt|Goodbye.}}
** '''Player:''' Goodbye.
** '''Gregg:''' So long, human! I'll be here a little while longer if you want a teleport. Otherwise I'll see you in Lumbridge!
** {{tact|end}}

